stateDiagram-v2

    Red --> Green : TrafficEvent#colon;#colon;TimerTick<br/>[ if ctx.tick_count >= 3 and state.is_safe_for_ns_green() ]
    Green --> Yellow : TrafficEvent#colon;#colon;TimerTick<br/>[ if ctx.tick_count >= 4 ]
    Green --> Red : TrafficEvent#colon;#colon;Emergency
    Yellow --> Red : TrafficEvent#colon;#colon;TimerTick<br/>[ if ctx.tick_count >= 1 ]
